{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>在情报传递过程中，为了防止情报被截获，往往需要对情报用一定的方式加密，简单的加密算法虽然不足以完全避免情报被破译，但仍然能防止情报被轻易的识别。我们给出一种最简的的加密方法，对给定的一个字符串，把其中从a-y，A-Y的字母用其后继字母替代，把z和Z用a和A替代，其他非字母字符不变，则可得到一个简单的加密字符串。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"密码翻译 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出每行字符串的加密字符串。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>输入一行，包含一个字符串，长度小于80个字符。<p>","examples":"<input>Hello! How are you!\n</input><output>Ifmmp! Ipx bsf zpv!\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1136","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}